'''-{zh-cn:伊丽莎白·玛丽·"莉兹"·特拉斯; zh-tw:伊麗莎白·瑪麗·「麗茲」·特拉斯; zh-hk:卓慧思}-'''<ref>{{LondonGazette |issue= 59418 |date= 2010-05-13 |startpage= 8744 |city=London |accessdate=2010-06-21 }}</ref><ref>{{LondonGazette |issue= 59418 |date= 2010-05-13 |startpage= 8744 |city=London |accessdate= 2010-06-22 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url= http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20160715/55361043 |title= 【改名的藝術】英國新內閣官方中文譯名一覽 |agency= [[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報]] |location= 香港 |date= 2016-07-15 |accessdate= 2016-07-16 |archive-date= 2017-10-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20171014133752/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20160715/55361043 |dead-url= no }}</ref>{{post-nominals|country=GBR|PC|MP}}（{{lang-en|'''Elizabeth Mary "Liz" Truss'''}}，{{bd|1975年|7月26日||catIdx=T}}），港澳譯作卓慧思，英國[[保守黨_(英國)|保守黨]]政治人物，现任外交、國協及發展事務大臣。2016年至2017年出任[[司法大臣_(英国)|司法大臣]]兼[[大法官_(英國)|大法官]]，她是一千多年来英国首任女性大法官（[[普罗旺斯的埃莉诺|普罗旺斯的埃莉诺]]1253年只是{{le|監印官|Lord Keeper of the Great Seal}}）。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/jul/21/liz-truss-first-ever-female-lord-chancellor-justice-secretary 
|title=Liz Truss sworn in as first ever female lord chancellor
|date=2016-07-21
|newspaper=《[[衛報|衛報]]》 |accessdate=2017-04-11 |archive-date=2020-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201013231141/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/jul/21/liz-truss-first-ever-female-lord-chancellor-justice-secretary |dead-url=no }}</ref>在2017年6月的內閣改組中，她調任[[財政部首席秘書|財政部首席秘書]]。

1996年在[[牛津大學|牛津大學]]畢業后，特拉斯於投身商场任經濟師，后来成為{{link-en|改革 (智庫)|Reform (think tank)|改革智庫}}的副主任，直到[[2010年英国大选|2010年大选]]进入国会擔任下議院[[西南諾福克_(英國國會選區)|西南諾福克選區]]議員。作為[[後座議員|後座議員]]，特拉斯呼籲在一些政策領域包括兒童保育、數學教育和經濟進行改革<ref name="The lady's for turning">{{cite news |title=The lady's for turning, right from CND to Conservative |first=Anushka |last=Asthana |url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/politics/article3440383.ece |newspaper=[[The_Times|The Times]] |date=2012-06-09 |accessdate=2012-07-30 |archive-date=2016-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314142729/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/politics/article3440383.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>，又成立了保守黨議員的自由企業小組。同時，她撰寫和合作撰寫了許多文章和書籍，例如《聯盟之後》（''After the Coalition''；2011年）及《{{le|釋放不列顛|Britannia Unchained}}》（''Britannia Unchained''；2012年）。

2012年9月，特拉斯獲委任為[[英國教育部|英國教育部]]分管教育及兒童保育的{{le|政務次官|Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State}}<ref name="DfE biography">{{cite web |url=https://education.gov.uk/aboutdfe/departmentalinformation/ministerialteam/truss |title=Elizabeth Truss MP |year=2012 |publisher=[[Department_for_Education|Department for Education]] |accessdate=2012-09-11 |archive-date=2012-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121030152821/https://www.education.gov.uk/aboutdfe/departmentalinformation/ministerialteam/truss |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年被时任[[英国首相|首相]][[戴维·卡梅伦|戴维·卡梅伦]]提拔进[[英国内阁|内阁]]担任环境、食品和郊野事务大臣。2016年7月，大衛·卡麥隆辭任[[英國首相|英國首相]]，特拉斯獲新任首相[[文翠珊|文翠珊]]委任，接替[[高文浩|高文浩]]任[[大法官_(英國)|大法官]]兼司法大臣。<ref>{{Cite news |url= http://tw.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20160714/bknint-20160714192722621-0714_17011_001.html |title= 新任英揆重組內閣　卓慧思成首位女大法官 |agency= [[東方日報_(香港)|東網台灣]] |location= 台灣 |date= 2016-07-14 |accessdate= 2016-07-16 |archive-date= 2016-08-28 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160828165430/http://tw.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20160714/bknint-20160714192722621-0714_17011_001.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>
2021年9月16日，英國首相強森大幅改組內閣，卓慧思被調任為外交、國協及發展事務大臣，接替出任為副首相的多米尼克·拉布。

== 早年生活和教育 ==

特拉斯出生于英国[[牛津|牛津]]。她在一个北方的左翼家庭被抚养长大；她的父亲约翰·-{特拉斯}-是[[利兹大学|利兹大学]][[纯粹数学|纯粹数学]]教授；她的母亲是一位护士和教师，还是[[核裁军运动|核裁军运动]]的成员。<ref name="Times profile">{{cite news |title=Profile: Elizabeth Truss |url=http://www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/sto/Test/politics/article189702.ece |newspaper=[[The_Sunday_Times|The Sunday Times]] |date=2009-11-08 |accessdate=2012-07-30 |archive-date=2015-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150601071911/http://www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/sto/Test/politics/article189702.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>特拉斯称自己的双亲为“[[英国工党|工党]]左派”。<ref name="The lady's for turning" />当特拉斯后来竞选议会席位，她的母亲同意支持她的运动，她的父亲拒绝这样做。<ref name="The lady's for turning" /><ref>{{cite news |title=Next right |first=James |last=Forsyth |url=http://www.spectator.co.uk/issues/23-june-2012/next-right |newspaper=[[The_Spectator|The Spectator]] |date=2012-06-23 |accessdate=2012-07-30 |archive-date=2021-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211105085955/https://www.spectator.co.uk/issues/23-june-2012/next-right }}</ref>

特拉斯在[[苏格兰|苏格兰]][[佩斯利|佩斯利]]的国立小学就读，<ref name="The lady's for turning" />又升入东北利兹的{{le|综合学校|Comprehensive school}}朗德黑学校就读。她在加拿大居住了一年，并将在那里学习的竞争态度与利兹接受的“新潮”教育进行了对比。<ref name="The lady's for turning" />1993年她进入[[牛津大学默顿学院|牛津大学默顿学院]]学习[[哲学、政治学及经济学|哲学、政治学及经济学]]。

== 早年事业 ==

1996年毕业后，特拉斯先后进入[[荷兰皇家壳牌|荷兰皇家壳牌]]担任商务经理，{{le|大东环球|Cable & Wireless Worldwide}}任经济主管，后升任合格的[[管理会计|管理会计]]。<ref>[http://www.elizabethtruss.com/about-elizabeth-truss-0 "Biography"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.elizabethtruss.com/about-elizabeth-truss-0 |date=20140716060605 }}, Elizabeth Truss' official website</ref>

2008年，特拉斯两次参选国会议员失败，遂成为{{link-en|改革 (智庫)|Reform (think tank)|改革智庫}}的副主任，<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/profile/elizabeth-truss |title=Guardian contributor page |work=The Guardian |accessdate=2014-07-15 |archive-date=2019-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513082317/https://www.theguardian.com/profile/elizabeth-truss |dead-url=no }}</ref>她在学校提倡更严格的学术标准，更加重视打击严重和有组织的犯罪行为，并采取紧急行动来应对英国的竞争力下降。她共同撰写了《数学价值》<ref>[http://www.reform.co.uk/pages/2145/view "The value of mathematics"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reform.co.uk/pages/2145/view |date=20120406100205 }}, Reform, June 2008</ref>和《新水平》<ref>[http://www.reform.co.uk/pages/2152/view "A new level"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reform.co.uk/pages/2152/view |date=20120406100248 }}, Reform, June 2009</ref>等报告。

== 政治事业 ==

特拉斯是[[牛津大学|牛津大学]]自由民主党主席，是青年和学生联盟全国执行委员会成员。她在1994年的自民党年会上表达了{{le|共和派|Republicanism in the United Kingdom}}的观点。<ref>[http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/politics/article4149530.ece Truss flirted with Lib Dems before embracing Tories] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/politics/article4149530.ece |date=20150601062742 }}, ''[[The_Times|The Times]]'', 17 July 2014</ref><ref>[https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2012/sep/24/liberal-democrat-conference-roy-jenkins Liberal Democrat conference: the spirit of Roy Jenkins lives on] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2012/sep/24/liberal-democrat-conference-roy-jenkins |date=20211105095833 }}, ''[[卫报|卫报]]'', 4 September 2012</ref>特拉斯于1996年加入保守党。<ref name="Democracy Live profile">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/democracylive/hi/representatives/profiles/40370.stm |title=Elizabeth Truss MP |work=BBC Democracy Live |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2010-07-25 |archive-date=2014-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140717090407/http://news.bbc.co.uk/democracylive/hi/representatives/profiles/40370.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>她从1998年至2000年担任[[刘易舍姆德特福德_(英国国会选区)|刘易舍姆德特福德]]选区保守协会的主席。<ref name="Democracy Live profile" />2006年，特拉斯当选为伦敦[[格林威治|格林威治]]市议员，于2010年任满离任。

=== 国会议员候选人 ===

2001年，特拉斯出马[[西约克郡|西约克郡]]的[[赫姆斯沃思_(英国国会选区)|赫姆斯沃思]]选区，在这个工党的铁票仓，特拉斯以4%选票之差落败。<ref name=BT30460377/>这引起了[[保守党中央党部|保守党中央党部]]的注意，中央党部指派特拉斯担任国会议员[[马克·菲尔德|马克·菲尔德]]的资深政治顾问，后来她与菲尔德陷入婚外情。<ref name=BT30460377/>2005年，西约克郡的[[科尔德河谷_(英国国会选区)|科尔德河谷]]选区的国会议员苏·卡特琳被当地的保守党协会罢免，[[2005年英国大选|当年大选]]特拉斯被指名出马参选该选区。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1480977/Dumped-candidate-blames-old-Tory-sexism.html|title=Dumped candidate blames old Tory sexism|first=By Paul|last=Stokes|publisher=|accessdate=2017-04-11|archive-date=2019-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517070628/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1480977/Dumped-candidate-blames-old-Tory-sexism.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>但当地保守党协会的分裂导致工党议员当选。<ref>[https://www.theguardian.com/politics/person/9162/elizabeth-truss "Electoral History and Profile"], ''The Guardian''</ref>

戴维·卡梅伦[[保守党领袖_(英国)|党领袖]]任内，特拉斯被列入有争议的{{le|A名单|A-List (Conservative)}}中。<ref name=BT30460377/>2006年，保守党的安全选区大伦敦[[布罗姆利和奇斯尔赫斯特_(英国国会选区)|布罗姆利和奇斯尔赫斯特]]选区的国会议员{{le|埃里克·富特|Eric Forth}}逝世，特拉斯被派往参加补选的党内初选。《[[每日邮报|每日邮报]]》揭露了她与马克·菲尔德的婚外情故事，<ref name=edp30oct09/><ref>{{cite news|last=Rayner|first=Gordon|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/9668355/MPs-involved-in-scandals-accused-of-hypocrisy-over-calls-for-tougher-regulation-of-the-press.html?iframe=true&width=90%&height=90%|title=MPs involved in scandals accused of 'hypocrisy' over calls for tougher regulation of the press|work=The Daily Telegraphdate=9 November 2012|accessdate=2016-12-08|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021172840/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/9668355/MPs-involved-in-scandals-accused-of-hypocrisy-over-calls-for-tougher-regulation-of-the-press.html?iframe=true&width=90%25&height=90%25|dead-url=no}}</ref>结果大伦敦议会保守党领袖[[鲍伯·尼尔|鲍伯·尼尔]]赢得初选。<ref name=BT30460377>{{cite web|url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/life/features/a-political-affair-we-profile-cabinet-minister-liz-truss-30460377.html|title=A political affair: We profile cabinet minister Liz Truss - BelfastTelegraph.co.uk|publisher=|accessdate=2017-04-11|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202094642/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/life/features/a-political-affair-we-profile-cabinet-minister-liz-truss-30460377.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2009年，特拉斯被[[西南诺福克_(英国国会选区)|西南诺福克]]选区的保守党协会选为党内初选候选人之一，她在第一轮投票中就以超过50%的得票率击败其他五位候选人当选。<ref name=telegraph13nov09>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/6554080/David-Cameron-phones-local-grandee-to-try-to-save-Elizabeth-Truss-from-deselection.html "David Cameron phones local grandee"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/6554080/David-Cameron-phones-local-grandee-to-try-to-save-Elizabeth-Truss-from-deselection.html |date=20201026160616 }}, ''The Daily Telegraph'', 13 November 2009</ref><ref>[http://iaindale.blogspot.co.uk/2009/10/edp-column-why-liz-truss-deserves.html "Iain Dale's EDP column"] {{Wayback|url=http://iaindale.blogspot.co.uk/2009/10/edp-column-why-liz-truss-deserves.html |date=20180224131534 }}, ''Eastern Daily Press'', 31 October 2009</ref>选举结束后不久，选区保守党协会的一些成员反对特拉斯的当选，声称有关她不忠的信息已经给协会其他会员留下不佳的印象。<ref name=edp30oct09>{{cite news|url=http://www.edp24.co.uk/news/tory_s_affair_details_withheld_at_meeting_1_524413|title=Tory's affair details 'withheld at meeting|work=Eastern Daily Press|date=2009-10-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408214413/http://www.edp24.co.uk/news/tory_s_affair_details_withheld_at_meeting_1_524413|archivedate=2014-04-08|accessdate=2017-04-11}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=McSmith|first=Andy|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/a-field-day-for-the-tory-old-guard-1821258.html|title=A field day for the Tory old guard|work=The Independent|date=2009-11-16|accessdate=2017-04-11|archive-date=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213163151/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/a-field-day-for-the-tory-old-guard-1821258.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>提出动议终止特拉斯的候选人资格，但三星期后，选区保守党协会全会以132票对37票否决了这个动议。<ref name=bbc17nov09>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/norfolk/8363403.stm|title=Tory woman wins selection battle|publisher=BBC News|date=2009-11-17|accessdate=2017-04-11|archive-date=2017-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170813233126/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/norfolk/8363403.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 国会事业 ==
[[File:Liz_Truss_MP,_Minister_for_Education_and_Childcare,_at_her_speech_setting_out_government_plans_to_promote_more_great_childcare_(8427105682).jpg|upright]]
2010年5月6日，特拉斯当选为国会议员，当选后，她致力于为位于自己选区的{{le|马厄姆皇家空军基地|RAF Marham}}保留[[狂风战斗机|狂风战斗机]]，<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-norfolk-11749819 "Campaign aim to keep Tornado base at RAF Marham"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-norfolk-11749819 |date=20190520081741 }}, BBC News, 13 November 2010</ref>七个多月的时间里，她在下院提出了十三个关于马汉姆皇家空军基地的问题，就这一问题进行了特别辩论，向大臣们发了几十封信，并转交了一份递交给[[唐宁街|唐宁街]]的请愿书。<ref name="bbc.co.uk">[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-28355481 "Elizabeth Truss joins the cabinet table in reshuffle"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-28355481 |date=20190624193952 }}, BBC News, 18 July 2014</ref>她也成功游说了A11公路西移以保护{{le|塞特福德森林|Thetford Forest}}。<ref>[http://www.edp24.co.uk/news/crime/former_minister_s_regret_over_a11_dualling_1_833276 "Former minister’s regret over A11 dualling"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.edp24.co.uk/news/crime/former_minister_s_regret_over_a11_dualling_1_833276 |date=20160416074929 }}, EDP, 17 March 2011</ref>这座英国最大的低地森林在她的选区里，她并提出反对出售森林的建议，<ref>[http://www.edp24.co.uk/news/politics/government_urged_to_grant_heritage_status_to_thetford_forest_1_791130 "Government urged to grant heritage status to Thetford Forest"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.edp24.co.uk/news/politics/government_urged_to_grant_heritage_status_to_thetford_forest_1_791130 |date=20160416044416 }}, EDP, 2 February 2011</ref>并在防止在西诺福克建造垃圾焚烧炉发挥了主导作用。<ref name="bbc.co.uk"/>她为她选区的工作，特别是A47的路口设计改善，2013年1月，她因此被道路安全慈善组织{{le|刹车 (慈善)|Brake (charity)|刹车}}评选为道路安全议员。<ref>[http://www.brake.org.uk/parliamentarian-awards/etruss.htm "Road Safety Parliamentarian of the Month"] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20130423185719/http://www.brake.org.uk/parliamentarian-awards/etruss.htm |date=2013-04-23 }}, Brake, January 2013</ref>

2011年3月，她为自由智囊团{{le|教育政策研究所|Education Policy Institute}}撰写了一篇论文，论证了结束对教育系统中严重学术科目的偏见，从而改善社会流动性的必要性。<ref>[http://www.centreforum.org/index.php/mainpublications/29-academic-rigour-social-mobility "Academic rigour and social mobility: how low income students are being kept out of top jobs"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.centreforum.org/index.php/mainpublications/29-academic-rigour-social-mobility |date=20120419232456 }}, CentreForum, 15 March 2011</ref>特拉斯在2012年5月为同一智库写了另一篇文章，她主张改变英国儿童保育市场的结构。<ref>[http://www.centreforum.org/assets/pubs/affordable-quality.pdf "Affordable quality: new approaches to childcare"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.centreforum.org/assets/pubs/affordable-quality.pdf |date=20161109024357 }}, CentreForum, May 2012</ref>

2011年10月，她创立了由其他40多名保守党议员支持的自由企业小组。<ref>[http://www.freeenterprise.org.uk/ "Free Enterprise Group"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.freeenterprise.org.uk/ |date=20201204230848 }}, FEG website</ref>2011年9月，与自由企业小组四名成员一道，她共同撰写了《聯盟之後》之后，这本书试图挑战一个共识，即认为英国的经济衰退是不可避免的，因为英国争取到了更多的创业者和精英文化的回归。<ref>[http://www.bitebackpublishing.com/products/40/ "After the Coalition"]{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}, Biteback Publishing, 16 September 2011</ref>另一卷题为《{{le|釋放不列顛|Britannia Unchained}}》的论文“面对未来不确定性，对英国面临的挑战进行了深刻而重要的评估”，于2012年9月发布。<ref>[http://www.palgrave.com/booksellers/sellin/Britannia-Unchained.pdf "Britannia Unchained"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.palgrave.com/booksellers/sellin/Britannia-Unchained.pdf |date=20121028175455 }}, Palgrave Macmillan</ref>作为《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》专栏的一部分，特拉斯写了一篇文章，扼要介绍了她关于科学在教育中的重要性论文的部分章节。<ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/science/9517706/We-must-shift-science-out-of-the-geek-ghetto.html "We must shift science out of the geek ghetto"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/science/9517706/We-must-shift-science-out-of-the-geek-ghetto.html |date=20140611234423 }}, ''The Daily Telegraph'', 4 September 2012</ref>该作品被物理学家[[布萊恩·考克斯_(物理學家)|布莱恩·考克斯]]誉为“优秀文章”。<ref>[https://twitter.com/ProfBrianCox/status/242942710514855937 "Brian Cox tweet"] {{Wayback|url=https://twitter.com/ProfBrianCox/status/242942710514855937 |date=20160413094214 }}, Twitter, 4 September 2012</ref>

特拉斯支持英国遵循德国的成例，允许人们免税和不太规范的“[[迷你工作|迷你工作]]”。<ref>{{cite news |title=Treasury considers bid to boost employment with tax-free 'mini-jobs' |first=Juliette |last=Jowit |url=https://www.theguardian.com/society/2012/aug/19/treasury-boost-employment-mini-jobs |newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=2012-08-19 |accessdate=2012-09-08 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111190849/http://www.theguardian.com/society/2012/aug/19/treasury-boost-employment-mini-jobs |dead-url=no }}</ref>由于特拉斯于2012年2月发布了一份关于自由企业集团政策的文件，该文件后来被财政部采纳为促进增长的政策。<ref>{{cite news |title=Treasury 'considers tax-free mini-jobs to spur employment' |first1=Rachel |last1=Cooper |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/economics/9486693/Treasury-considers-tax-free-mini-jobs-to-spur-employment.html |newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |date=2012-08-20 |accessdate=2012-09-08 |archive-date=2020-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026164133/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/economics/9486693/Treasury-considers-tax-free-mini-jobs-to-spur-employment.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Treasury weighs German 'mini jobs' scheme |first1=Helen |last1=Warrell |first2=Chris |last2=Bryant |url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/30c22eda-ea18-11e1-929b-00144feab49a.html |newspaper=[[Financial_Times|Financial Times]] |date=2012-08-19 |accessdate=2012-09-08 |archive-date=2012-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121029192518/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/30c22eda-ea18-11e1-929b-00144feab49a.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

特拉斯发动了改进学校课程使之更严格的运动，特别是数学教学。她指出只有20％的英国学生学习数学到18岁，<ref name="Norfolk MP calls for">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-17538107|title=Norfolk MP calls for cash for maths|last=McGurran|first=Deborah|date=2012-03-28|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2012-07-30|archive-date=2019-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190519001558/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-17538107|dead-url=no}}</ref>并呼吁全日制教育中的数学课程应该改为强制性的。<ref>{{cite news |title=Maths should be compulsory until 18, says MP report |first=Sean |last=Coughlan |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/education-18522634 |publisher=BBC News |date=2012-06-21 |accessdate=2012-07-30 |archive-date=2015-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925150806/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/education-18522634 |dead-url=no }}</ref>特拉斯自己拿到了两张数学[[普通教育高级程度证书|普通教育高级程度证书]]（A级考试）。<ref name="Norfolk MP calls for" />她认为，综合学校学生正在被“骗售”得更容易，他们被授以低质量的知识，学校以此来提高自己而不是学生的成绩：据媒体研究，在私立学校的学生普通教育高级程度证书考试的通过率比综合学校学生高六倍。<ref>{{cite news |title=Comprehensive school pupils 'mis-sold' soft A-level courses |first=Graeme |last=Paton |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/educationnews/8575270/Comprehensive-school-pupils-mis-sold-soft-A-level-courses.html |newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |date=2011-06-15 |accessdate=2012-07-30 |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031143320/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/educationnews/8575270/Comprehensive-school-pupils-mis-sold-soft-A-level-courses.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>特拉斯也批评过度依赖计算器损害了心算能力。<ref>{{cite news |title=Elizabeth Truss in a calculated move on maths |first=Deborah |last=McGurran |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-15994164 |publisher=BBC News |date=2011-12-01 |accessdate=2012-07-30 |archive-date=2019-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190519142503/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-15994164 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

自2011年3月起，特拉斯任下院{{le|司法专责委员会|Justice Select Committee}}委员，<ref>[http://www.parliament.uk/business/committees/committees-a-z/commons-select/justice-committee/membership/ "Justice committee – membership"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.parliament.uk/business/committees/committees-a-z/commons-select/justice-committee/membership/ |date=20111121234238 }}, UK Parliament, March 2011</ref>直到2012年进入政府担任政务次官。

=== 教育部政务次官 ===
2012年9月4日，特拉斯被任命为教育部政务次官，负责育儿和早教、评估、资格和课程改革、表现和出勤以及学校食品审查。<ref>[https://www.gov.uk/government/people/elizabeth-truss "Parliamentary Under Secretary of State for Education and Childcare"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/people/elizabeth-truss |date=20210203050649 }}, gov.uk website. Retrieved 13 February 2014.</ref>任职期间，她发展了一些她所追求的政策领域。

2013年1月，她通过在两年制课程结束时集中考试，提出改革A级考试的建议。<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/democracylive/21160860 "A-level shake up will 'end the treadmill' of repeated exams"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/democracylive/21160860 |date=20190607193656 }}, BBC Democracy Live, 23 January 2013</ref>她试图提高英国数学的教学质量，担心英国学生落后于亚洲国家的同龄人，<ref>[https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2014/jul/15/liz-truss-media-personality-schooling-tory-conservative "Liz Truss: strong media personality with big ideas on schooling"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2014/jul/15/liz-truss-media-personality-schooling-tory-conservative |date=20210126113723 }}, ''The Guardian'', 15 July 22014</ref>并于2014年2月对[[上海|上海]]的[[上海师范大学|上海师范大学]]、[[上海中学|上海中学]]、[[建平中学|建平中学]]西校、福山外国语小学和上海市教育科学研究院进行了实地考察访问，以了解中国儿童如何成为世界上数学成绩最好的孩子。<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/education-26228234 "Shanghai visit for minister to learn maths lessons"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/education-26228234 |date=20191104011039 }}, BBC News, 18 February 2014</ref>

特拉斯还概述了改革保育计划，旨在大修保育资格，并为父母提供更多的优质教育和照料服务。<ref>[https://www.theguardian.com/money/2013/jan/29/childcare-restrictions-relaxed-minister-announces "Childcare restrictions to be relaxed, minister announces"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/money/2013/jan/29/childcare-restrictions-relaxed-minister-announces |date=20201027133528 }}, ''The Guardian'', 29 January 2013</ref>拟议的改革受到一些组织的普遍欢迎，例如慈善机构{{le|4儿童|4Children}}、<ref>[http://www.education.gov.uk/inthenews/inthenews/a00220984/parents-choice-hq-childcare "Parents to have more choice of high quality childcare"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.education.gov.uk/inthenews/inthenews/a00220984/parents-choice-hq-childcare |date=20130201143232 }}, Department for Education, 29 January 2013</ref>{{le|英国工业联合会|Confederation of British Industry}}<ref>[http://www.daynurseries.co.uk/news/article.cfm/id/1558751/coalition-promises-more-great-childcare-but-growing-anxiety-in-the-nursery-sector "Coalition promises 'More Great Childcare' amid growing anxiety in the nursery sector"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.daynurseries.co.uk/news/article.cfm/id/1558751/coalition-promises-more-great-childcare-but-growing-anxiety-in-the-nursery-sector |date=20201125053131 }}, daynurseries.co.uk, 29 January 2013</ref>和{{le|西英格兰学院|College of West Anglia}}。<ref>[http://www.lynnnews.co.uk/news/latest-news/king-s-lynn-college-supports-childcare-changes-1-4768197 "College supports childcare changes"] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.today/20130421093240/http://www.lynnnews.co.uk/news/latest-news/king-s-lynn-college-supports-childcare-changes-1-4768197 |date=2013-04-21 }}, Lynn News, 8 February 2013</ref>但是，这些提案遇到了他人的反对。英国劳工联合会议总书记{{le|弗朗西斯·奥格雷迪|Frances O'Grady}}和当时的影子教育大臣[[史提夫·特维格|史提夫·特维格]]是批评改革的人之一，<ref>[http://www.channel4.com/news/childcare-plans-will-hit-standards-labour-warns "Childcare plans will hit standards, Labour warns"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.channel4.com/news/childcare-plans-will-hit-standards-labour-warns |date=20201130054508 }}, Channel 4 News, 29 January 2013</ref>还有一些家长和保育机构，如慈善机构国家托儿所协会。<ref>[http://www.ndna.org.uk/news/press+releases/January+2013/More-Great-Childcare "Quality of early education must not be sacrificed if we want More Great Childcare says national charity"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ndna.org.uk/news/press+releases/January+2013/More-Great-Childcare |date=20141018122753 }}, NDNA, 29 January 2013</ref>

专栏作家{{le|波利·汤因比|Polly Toynbee}}非常批评大臣的计划，<ref>[https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2013/jan/29/hofit-six-toddlers-in-bugy-truss-childcare "How do you fit six toddlers into a buggy? Ask Liz Truss"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2013/jan/29/hofit-six-toddlers-in-bugy-truss-childcare |date=20190513104547 }}, ''The Guardian'', 29 January 2013</ref>并质问特拉斯自己如何照顾两个婴儿与四个孩子。特拉斯对汤因比作出了回应，认为作为一名早教工作者是一项标准非常苛刻的职业，需要很高的专业知识，而且指责汤因比没有接受过专业培训。<ref>[https://www.theguardian.com/money/2013/jan/29/childcare-reform-proposals-fierce-criticism "Childcare reform proposals face fierce criticism"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/money/2013/jan/29/childcare-reform-proposals-fierce-criticism |date=20201112013531 }}, ''The Guardian'', 29 January 2013</ref>事实上，时任[[英国副首相|副首相]][[尼克·克莱格|尼克·克莱格]]阻止了放宽保育的改革建议。<ref>[http://news.sky.com/story/1100006/childcare-ratio-shake-up-blocked-by-clegg "Childcare Ratio Shake-Up Blocked By Clegg"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.sky.com/story/1100006/childcare-ratio-shake-up-blocked-by-clegg |date=20160304093739 }}, Sky News, 6 June 2013</ref>

=== 环境、食品及乡郊事务大臣 ===

