uss_1_3695810 "Tokenism, climate change, King’s Lynn incinerator, farming and food: Q&A with Environment Secretary and Norfolk MP Elizabeth Truss"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.edp24.co.uk/business/farming-news/tokenism_climate_change_king_s_lynn_incinerator_farming_and_food_q_a_with_environment_secretary_and_norfolk_mp_elizabeth_truss_1_3695810 |date=20150405021635 }}, Eastern Daily Press, 25 July 2014</ref>

